p: The title compound was obtained in 35% yield from compound 33 followed the general procedure for Suzuki arylation: 1H NMR (300 MHz, CDCl 3) δ 3.85 (s, 3H), 3.92 (s, 3H), 4.65 (s, 2H), 6.58 (dd, J = 0.9, 7.8 Hz, 1H), 7.05 (d, J = 8.1 Hz, 1H), 7.13 (d, J = 8.4 Hz, 2H), 7.33 (d, J = 7.8 Hz, 1H), 7.41–7.46 (m, 2H), 7.52 (d, J = 8.4 Hz, 2H), 8.04 (d, J = 8.4 Hz, 2H), 8.20 (d, J = 2.1 Hz, 1H), 8.98 (d, J = 2.1 Hz, 1H).
